message.content:
The kitchen and dining area form an L‐shaped space with dark cabinets and a white refrigerator in one corner. Along the beige countertop under the upper black cabinets, several items are arranged side by side: a jar of strawberry jam, a box labeled “Jell‐O,” a container of “Alpen Salz,” a short stack of white plates, a box labeled “Rice Bubbles,” and another box labeled “Chucky Mania.” Near the corner cooktop sits a small metal pot, with a single mug just beside it. A wooden range hood is mounted above, and a stainless steel sink with a faucet is set into the same countertop beneath a wooden‐framed window.

Moving into the adjoining dining area, a rectangular wooden table stands at the center, surrounded by white, high‐backed chairs. On the table, a large water bottle labeled “Evian” rests partially within a white fruit bowl containing several round fruits; to one side of these sits a black rectangular box of shortbread. Nearby are a clear glass pitcher and a single wine glass. A white door with a metallic handle is positioned on the right‐hand wall, and the floor throughout is a parquet wood finish.
